   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject Two Hundred Six THE WATER OF THE FOUNTAIN OF LIFE Scripture: Rev 7:17; 21:6; 22:1, 17 The fountain of life God is the fountain of life.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>This fountain issues from the Son of God.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>God is in His Son Jesus Christ as the fountain of life.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>The water of the fountain of life The water of the fountain of life is the life of God.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>This water of life is flowing out of God s Son to be received by man.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>The function of the water of life As water is for quenching thirst, so also is the water of life.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>It quenches the thirst of human living.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>Water is not only for quenching thirst, but also for enjoyment.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>So also is the water of life to man.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>It not only quenches man s thirst, but also gives man eternal enjoyment.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>The water of life also delivers man from death.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>How to obtain the water of life To obtain water you must drink.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>You do not need to pay any price because it is freely given by God.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>Everyone can drink freely.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>To drink freely is not to depend on your works, but simply to believe and receive.</S>
   </TEXT>
